                        <h1>
                            Change of Name: The Ministry of Labour and Social Affairs </h1>
                    
                
            </div>
        </div>
    

<div class="documentBody" id="Tekstinnhold">
    
        <div class="imagecontainer">
            <img id="FullRegion_CenterAndRightRegion_CenterRegion_ctl00_ucRegjeringenNormalPresentation_innholdsbildeImg" title="Picture of The Ministry of Labour and Social Affairs. Address: Akersgata 64, Oslo, Norway" class="contentImage" src="/upload/AD/nyhetsbilder/2013/Akersgata_64_534x270.jpg" alt="Picture of The Ministry of Labour and Social Affairs. Address: Akersgata 64, Oslo, Norway" />
            <p class="imagetext">
                </p>
        </div>
    
    
    
        <div>
            

<div>
	<p><strong>The Ministry of Labour changes name to The Ministry of Labour and Social Affairs 01.01.2014.</strong></p>
<p>The Ministry’s responsibilities will remain the same.</p>
<p>The change of name will not affect the postal address or phone numbers to the Ministry. All email addresses, however, will change to @asd.dep.no</p>
<h2>Read more</h2>
<p><a href="/en/dep/asd/about-the-ministry.html?id=170">About the Ministry</a></p>
